  "texts": [
    "Some of the questions might seem like formalities, but they can significantly affect the board's work.",
    "For example, if the necessary majority or the quorum are too high, the board might not be able to adopt certain decisions.",
    "This could bias the board toward inaction.",
    "Similarly, if the board is not able to convene ad hoc meetings or only upon request by the company, it might not be able to respond adequately to emergencies.",
    "Enforceability of decisionsAnother question is to what extent the board's decisions should be enforceable."
  ],
